  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/885570/extras/3de6370a7c1aef32d515056232ce94f3.avif?t=1771038065\" width=600 height=260 /></span><br><br>Nova-Life is a simulation video game mainly focused on city roleplay in an open world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE FIRST FRENCH ROLEPLAY GAME!</h2><br>In Nova-Life you can create your own character, find a job and go to work to gain money.<br><br>The Nova-Life project will have around ten dozen or so jobs in its final version, including the possibility of becoming a self-entrepreneur in order to create your own store, and/or your own company which will offer a wide range of choices in the roleplay.<br><br>The roleplay of Nova-Life is a French roleplay.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Features </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A pleasant driving system<br></li><li> Written communication and VO-IP<br></li><li> Multiple vehicles<br></li><li> Many professions</li></ul><br><strong> The jobs have a level hierarchy, which allows you to get a rank in your job and therefore increase your salary </strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/885570/extras/3de6370a7c1aef32d515056232ce94f3.avif?t=1771038065\" width=600 height=260 /></span><br><br>Nova-Life is a simulation video game mainly focused on city roleplay in an open world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE FIRST FRENCH ROLEPLAY GAME!</h2><br>In Nova-Life you can create your own character, find a job and go to work to gain money.<br><br>The Nova-Life project will have around ten dozen or so jobs in its final version, including the possibility of becoming a self-entrepreneur in order to create your own store, and/or your own company which will offer a wide range of choices in the roleplay.<br><br>The roleplay of Nova-Life is a French roleplay.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Features </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A pleasant driving system<br></li><li> Written communication and VO-IP<br></li><li> Multiple vehicles<br></li><li> Many professions</li></ul><br><strong> The jobs have a level hierarchy, which allows you to get a rank in your job and therefore increase your salary </strong>",
